Chicken Marsala with Fettuccine
Tender chicken breast with sauteed baby bell mushrooms cooked in a combination of rich stock
and Marsala wine then tossed with freshly made fettuccine pasta
Chicken Piccata with Fettuccine
Starting with chicken breast that has been sauteed until succulent in a delicious sauce made with
butter, white wine and capers then sliced and tossed in our freshly made fettuccine pasta
Cheesecake
This is a cheesecake like no other, with a soft cream mix that’s perfectly formed to create a sinfully
delicate texture, it’s the best made-from-scratch cheesecake you will ever have!
Chicken & Potato Gnocchi Soup
An Italian version of chicken and dumpling soup with freshly made
gnocchi, and tender chicken in a rich aromatic stock
Double Layer Carrot Cake
Just in time for spring this utterly delicious made from scratch moist and decadent carrot cake is
nut free and raisin free and iced over with a mixture of cream cheese and butter cream frosting.
Chicken Cacciatore Lasagna
As if lasagna couldn’t be more enticing, Chef Tony kicks it up and creates this delectable infusion.
Using tender braised chicken and familiar Cacciatore flavors layered between our made in house
fresh pasta and loaded with four classic Italian cheeses makes this lasagna luxuriously rich
Cavatelli Pasta with Puttanesca
This fragrant traditional Italian pasta sauce is made with fresh herbs, tomatoes, olives, capers, and
garlic then sauteed with our made-to-order Cavatelli pasta which is small pasta shells made from
semolina. It’s flavorful, comforting, and the perfect dish for a Sunday meal.
Our house made dough rolled up with a mix of seasonal vegetables

herbs.
